00:50:14.559 --> 00:50:17.190
need a touch from Jesus and they're

00:50:17.200 --> 00:50:18.870
desperate?'I

00:50:18.880 --> 00:50:20.630
know God stationed me in a little

00:50:20.640 --> 00:50:22.710
place to go to church over here

00:50:22.720 --> 00:50:25.349
and visit. And he said, 'Go back

00:50:25.359 --> 00:50:27.910
there and help them.

00:50:27.920 --> 00:50:29.910
Pray for

00:50:29.910 --> 00:50:29.920
them.'And

00:50:29.920 --> 00:50:32.870
I saw the youth coming in by the hundreds—not thousands

00:50:32.870 --> 00:50:32.880
because there are

00:50:32.880 --> 00:50:34.870
not thousands

00:50:34.880 --> 00:50:36.710
there—by

00:50:36.720 --> 00:50:40.230
the hundreds. But it takes one

00:50:40.230 --> 00:50:40.240
person;

00:50:40.240 --> 00:50:42.470
one person led Billy Graham to

00:50:42.480 --> 00:50:45.430
Jesus, and Billy Graham led

00:50:45.440 --> 00:50:48.150
millions.

00:50:48.160 --> 00:50:52.069
Who was the person that led my

00:50:52.079 --> 00:50:57.030
friends to Jesus? I must mess

00:50:57.040 --> 00:50:58.470
up his name again:

00:50:58.480 --> 00:51:00.390
Maldonado.

00:51:00.400 --> 00:51:05.109
Maldonado has led millions to Jesus.

00:51:05.119 --> 00:51:06.950
He talks about him. Maldonado is going to Brazil

00:51:06.960 --> 00:51:09.109
in a couple weeks.

00:51:09.119 --> 00:51:14.150
And who led him to Jesus?

00:51:14.160 --> 00:51:17.190
But it took one spark to spread a major

00:51:17.200 --> 00:51:21.349
fire.

00:51:21.359 --> 00:51:24.069
It takes one person

00:51:24.079 --> 00:51:27.670
to reach millions.

00:51:27.680 --> 00:51:32.390
And he says, 'I have somebody

00:51:32.400 --> 00:51:33.910
here.'So

00:51:33.920 --> 00:51:35.829
whatever your vision is, do it with all

00:51:35.839 --> 00:51:37.589
your heart. Don't do it halfway. It's

00:51:37.599 --> 00:51:40.069
like I told Pastor Chip, I said, 'We've got

00:51:40.079 --> 00:51:42.870
to make the greatest facility

00:51:42.880 --> 00:51:45.030
with what God has given us so that

00:51:45.040 --> 00:51:47.910
everybody in Oklahoma, Tulsa, and all

00:51:47.920 --> 00:51:50.069
these areas talk about how great

00:51:50.069 --> 00:51:50.079
the

00:51:50.079 --> 00:51:53.990
Collinsville, Oklahoma youth group is.'They are in

00:51:53.990 --> 00:51:54.000
a place with

00:51:54.000 --> 00:51:55.670
a population of hardly

00:51:55.680 --> 00:51:57.910
anybody; it has probably two

00:51:57.920 --> 00:51:59.670
stoplights.

00:51:59.680 --> 00:52:03.670
But why not do it and do it well?

00:52:03.680 --> 00:52:05.589
Why should we get the hand-me-downs

00:52:05.599 --> 00:52:07.190
in church and people go, 'Well, you

00:52:07.200 --> 00:52:09.349
know, it's just the youth'? No, it's the

00:52:09.359 --> 00:52:12.549
next generation.

00:52:12.559 --> 00:52:15.030
It's the next generation. For you were

00:52:15.040 --> 00:52:18.150
once a youth and so was I.

00:52:18.160 --> 00:52:20.549
So, that's why I try to tell you all

00:52:20.559 --> 00:52:21.990
a little bit more about

00:52:22.000 --> 00:52:23.990
me, but I don't know if

00:52:24.000 --> 00:52:25.109
you even wanted to hear that tonight,

00:52:25.119 --> 00:52:27.829
but people want to know about

00:52:27.839 --> 00:52:29.990
this kind of stuff I'm talking

00:52:30.000 --> 00:52:32.390
about. And I say it by the

00:52:32.390 --> 00:52:32.400
unction

00:52:32.400 --> 00:52:34.870
of the Holy Spirit.

00:52:34.880 --> 00:52:37.190
Be bold about what God's called you to

00:52:37.200 --> 00:52:39.349
do in these last days, but do it with

00:52:39.359 --> 00:52:41.349
all your heart.

00:52:41.359 --> 00:52:44.150
Get a backbone like a crowbar,

00:52:44.160 --> 00:52:46.870
get enthusiastic about it, and get

00:52:46.880 --> 00:52:50.950
some passion.

00:52:50.960 --> 00:52:52.230
Don't say, 'Well, it's just somebody

00:52:52.240 --> 00:52:54.470
else's

00:52:54.470 --> 00:52:54.480
responsibility.'When

00:52:54.480 --> 00:52:56.069
Jesus told me, he said, 'It's all

00:52:56.079 --> 00:52:57.910
hands on deck. Brandon, will you help me

00:52:57.920 --> 00:53:00.150
bring in the harvest?'I saw his

00:53:00.160 --> 00:53:02.790
hands, and Jesus was in the field. He

00:53:02.800 --> 00:53:04.950
was in overalls and he had a piece of

00:53:04.960 --> 00:53:06.950
wheat in his mouth and he put it up here.

00:53:06.960 --> 00:53:09.670
I saw the wheat

00:53:09.680 --> 00:53:11.910
bowing down and I saw harvest

00:53:11.920 --> 00:53:15.109
equipment, and the barn was full of

00:53:15.119 --> 00:53:16.630
the glory and the anointing. And he

00:53:16.640 --> 00:53:19.109
said, 'Do you see the angel armies that

00:53:19.119 --> 00:53:22.390
are coming? I've released the

00:53:22.400 --> 00:53:24.870
host of heaven to help you, for you're

00:53:24.880 --> 00:53:28.150
not alone. For there are more with you than there are with them.'You're not doing this alone, ladies and gentlemen, for there's more with you

00:53:28.160 --> 00:53:32.069
than there are with them.

00:53:36.079 --> 00:53:38.790
And I saw the

00:53:38.800 --> 00:53:41.589
angels and the host of heaven coming out,

00:53:41.599 --> 00:53:43.510
and they looked like a waterfall coming

00:53:43.520 --> 00:53:46.230
on this earth. And there

00:53:46.230 --> 00:53:46.240
were

00:53:46.240 --> 00:53:49.750
two angels per one unsaved person,

00:53:49.760 --> 00:53:51.430
and they were lined up. And he said,

00:53:51.440 --> 00:53:54.309
'I'm giving you a window of

00:53:54.319 --> 00:53:56.950
uninterrupted and unhindered. For Satan

00:53:56.960 --> 00:53:59.510
has blinded the eyes of the unbeliever,

00:53:59.520 --> 00:54:04.230
and I'm calling in the unsaved, for I've

00:54:04.240 --> 00:54:09.750
come to save that which was

00:54:09.750 --> 00:54:09.760
lost.'The

00:54:09.760 --> 00:54:12.470
harvest equipment is the anointing.

00:54:12.480 --> 00:54:15.109
And I saw Jesus walking amongst the

00:54:15.119 --> 00:54:17.750
wheat, and he was rubbing his hands all

00:54:17.760 --> 00:54:21.270
in it. And as I could see his

00:54:21.280 --> 00:54:23.910
hands rubbing through that wheat, he had

00:54:23.920 --> 00:54:27.030
massive holes in his hands,

00:54:27.040 --> 00:54:29.670
massive holes.

00:54:29.680 --> 00:54:32.069
And I could see through his hands. And I

00:54:32.079 --> 00:54:33.750
could see the wheat through his hands.

00:54:33.760 --> 00:54:35.829
And he said, 'Brandon, I

00:54:35.839 --> 00:54:39.030
suffered for every single one of them. I

00:54:39.040 --> 00:54:41.109
suffered for every single one of them.

00:54:41.119 --> 00:54:45.750
Help me bring in the harvest.

00:54:45.760 --> 00:54:49.910
Help me bring in the harvest.

00:54:49.920 --> 00:54:52.470
The harvest is plentiful and the

00:54:52.470 --> 00:54:52.480
laborers

00:54:52.480 --> 00:54:57.829
are few. Help me bring in the

00:54:57.829 --> 00:54:57.839
harvest.'I

00:54:57.839 --> 00:54:59.910
looked at him and I said, 'I'll do my

00:54:59.920 --> 00:55:02.790
best. As for me and my house, Lord, we

00:55:02.800 --> 00:55:04.630
will serve you. We will do whatever it

00:55:04.640 --> 00:55:07.589
takes to help bring in the

00:55:07.589 --> 00:55:07.599
harvest.'He

00:55:07.599 --> 00:55:10.230
said, 'I know you will.

00:55:10.240 --> 00:55:15.829
I know you

00:55:15.829 --> 00:55:15.839
will.'I'm

00:55:15.839 --> 00:55:17.829
just trying to tell you

00:55:17.839 --> 00:55:20.150
tonight

00:55:20.160 --> 00:55:22.069
there's so many things we can get stuck

00:55:22.079 --> 00:55:24.069
on.

00:55:24.079 --> 00:55:25.990
There's so many problems we have in our

00:55:25.990 --> 00:55:26.000
lives—the

00:55:26.000 --> 00:55:28.230
storms of life, the cares of

00:55:28.240 --> 00:55:30.230
this world that choke out everything and

00:55:30.240 --> 00:55:32.069
keep us distracted from what this

00:55:32.079 --> 00:55:34.150
person's saying or

00:55:34.150 --> 00:55:34.160
that

00:55:34.160 --> 00:55:36.309
person, and people persecute you

00:55:36.319 --> 00:55:37.670
for the word's sake. But it

00:55:37.670 --> 00:55:37.680
doesn't

00:55:37.680 --> 00:55:40.309
matter. All I know is when I stand

00:55:40.319 --> 00:55:42.870
before my Father, he'll judge me by

00:55:42.880 --> 00:55:44.390
what I've done for him and he'll look at

00:55:44.400 --> 00:55:46.230
me and say, 'Well done, thy good and

00:55:46.240 --> 00:55:49.430
faithful servant.'Or, 'Well,

00:55:49.440 --> 00:55:52.069
you could have done better.'But I don't

00:55:52.079 --> 00:55:53.589
want to stand before him and say, 'Hey,

00:55:53.599 --> 00:55:56.470
at least I

00:55:56.470 --> 00:55:56.480
tried.'I

00:55:56.480 --> 00:55:59.910
tried. I gave it all I got.

00:55:59.920 --> 00:56:01.750
I gave it all I got. And I want you to

00:56:01.760 --> 00:56:04.309
say that for your community. Help your

00:56:04.319 --> 00:56:07.030
pastors;

00:56:07.040 --> 00:56:09.349
help them.

00:56:09.359 --> 00:56:11.670
Don't sit idly by and say, 'Well, it's

00:56:11.680 --> 00:56:13.510
on

00:56:13.510 --> 00:56:13.520
them.'You

00:56:13.520 --> 00:56:17.030
know,

00:56:17.040 --> 00:56:18.789
'I

00:56:18.799 --> 00:56:20.549
work, whatever. I don't really have

00:56:20.559 --> 00:56:23.270
time to volunteer my

00:56:23.270 --> 00:56:23.280
time.'You

00:56:23.280 --> 00:56:25.510
know what? Everybody has the same

00:56:25.520 --> 00:56:28.549
hours a day.

00:56:28.559 --> 00:56:30.390
Everybody goes to work. Everybody

00:56:30.390 --> 00:56:30.400
busts

00:56:30.400 --> 00:56:32.950
their hiney to make ends meet

00:56:32.960 --> 00:56:35.990
for their home. But you can be a parking

00:56:36.000 --> 00:56:37.990
lot attendant. You can work being an

00:56:38.000 --> 00:56:40.230
usher at the door. There's something you

00:56:40.240 --> 00:56:42.630
can do to help your pastor.

00:56:42.640 --> 00:56:44.230
There's something you can do to help

00:56:44.240 --> 00:56:46.870
your local church and say, 'Hey,

00:56:46.880 --> 00:56:48.549
I'm going to pour myself

00:56:48.559 --> 00:56:51.430
out right here.'And it may just be

00:56:51.440 --> 00:56:54.470
picking up trash in the parking lot. And

00:56:54.480 --> 00:56:55.829
you say, 'Well, that's

00:56:55.829 --> 00:56:55.839
nothing.'But

00:56:55.839 --> 00:56:58.710
it's significant to the visitor

00:56:58.720 --> 00:57:00.950
that just showed up and said, 'You know

00:57:00.960 --> 00:57:02.069
what? They don't care about

00:57:02.079 --> 00:57:03.030
nothing. There's trash, there's

00:57:03.040 --> 00:57:04.630
cigarette butts, there's all kinds of

00:57:04.640 --> 00:57:06.309
stuff going on out here. This place is

00:57:06.319 --> 00:57:07.750
dirty. I don't ever want to come back here

00:57:07.750 --> 00:57:07.760
again.'The

00:57:07.760 --> 00:57:10.069
impression that you leave for

00:57:10.079 --> 00:57:12.470
the first impression when you walk in

00:57:12.480 --> 00:57:14.710
there could be what makes or breaks that

00:57:14.720 --> 00:57:17.109
person to give Jesus Christ a chance in

00:57:17.119 --> 00:57:18.950
their heart and say, 'Hey, I want to

00:57:18.960 --> 00:57:21.510
make him my Lord.'There's excellence in

00:57:21.520 --> 00:57:24.470
it. God's a God of excellence. That's

00:57:24.480 --> 00:57:26.630
why he talks to me all the time about my

00:57:26.640 --> 00:57:28.950
weight:

00:57:28.960 --> 00:57:31.829
'Brandon, I want you to be healthy.

00:57:31.839 --> 00:57:34.950
I don't want you to be obese. You

00:57:34.960 --> 00:57:38.470
display me on that camera to millions

00:57:38.480 --> 00:57:41.109
of people;

00:57:41.119 --> 00:57:42.870
I want you to take care of yourself.'And

00:57:42.870 --> 00:57:42.880
it isn't

00:57:42.880 --> 00:57:45.670
easy for Brandon.

00:57:45.680 --> 00:57:48.950
Today I had a smoothie and a wrap, but

00:57:48.960 --> 00:57:50.789
my flesh—whenever my daughter said,

00:57:50.799 --> 00:57:52.309
'Daddy, I want an ice cream,'I said,

00:57:52.319 --> 00:57:55.349
'Okay,

00:57:55.349 --> 00:57:55.359
honey.'But

00:57:55.359 --> 00:57:57.990
I'm learning to say it's good

00:57:58.000 --> 00:57:59.510
for you, but it's not good for me right

00:57:59.520 --> 00:58:01.829
now. I have to work

00:58:01.839 --> 00:58:03.910
out that stuff for Brandon

00:58:03.910 --> 00:58:03.920
Biggs.

00:58:03.920 --> 00:58:07.589
I'm just trying to be real with you

00:58:07.589 --> 00:58:07.599
all.

00:58:07.599 --> 00:58:09.589
But stretch your faith to believe God

00:58:09.599 --> 00:58:12.789
for more than just your

00:58:12.799 --> 00:58:14.870
needs.

00:58:14.880 --> 00:58:16.390
If you're just believing for your

00:58:16.400 --> 00:58:18.230
electric bill and your water and your

00:58:18.240 --> 00:58:20.630
gas and your house to be paid

00:58:20.640 --> 00:58:23.510
off or your car or whatever, believe

00:58:23.520 --> 00:58:26.630
God for your local church,

00:58:26.640 --> 00:58:28.549
that they're able to do outreaches like

00:58:28.559 --> 00:58:33.430
this, and pray for your people.

00:58:33.440 --> 00:58:36.630
Does it show the stadium?

00:58:36.640 --> 00:58:38.789
I get excited when I see the stadium. I love

00:58:38.799 --> 00:58:40.150
football. Football is my favorite time

00:58:40.160 --> 00:58:42.069
of year. I don't know about you, but I

00:58:42.079 --> 00:58:44.150
love football.

00:58:44.160 --> 00:58:53.190
Did you show it?

00:58:53.200 --> 00:58:56.150
Show just a little bit of that. Is that

00:58:56.160 --> 00:58:57.349
the church, right?

00:58:58.400 --> 00:59:05.990
Just play some of it.

00:59:06.000 --> 00:59:07.589
Just play fast clips like

00:59:07.599 --> 00:59:08.470
that.

00:59:08.480 --> 00:59:09.910
They're all showing up and they're

00:59:09.920 --> 00:59:12.390
all coming there. I'm just trying to

00:59:12.400 --> 00:59:15.270
say: come up with an idea for your local

00:59:15.280 --> 00:59:18.789
community. This is our idea.

00:59:18.789 --> 00:59:18.799
For

00:59:18.799 --> 00:59:20.390
those that have blessed our

00:59:20.400 --> 00:59:22.150
ministry, you've given into this and you

00:59:22.160 --> 00:59:24.630
don't even know it. I want to say

00:59:24.640 --> 00:59:27.270
thank you.

00:59:27.280 --> 00:59:28.870
There's a lot of kids that are getting

00:59:28.880 --> 00:59:30.870
saved and delivered there, and

00:59:30.880 --> 00:59:32.789
it's a blessing.

00:59:32.799 --> 00:59:35.109
I don't talk about stuff like

00:59:35.119 --> 00:59:38.069
that, but I'm just being real and

00:59:38.079 --> 00:59:39.910
transparent. The people who have blessed

00:59:39.920 --> 00:59:41.750
my ministry have given to

00:59:41.750 --> 00:59:41.760
this—a

00:59:41.760 --> 00:59:44.470
lot of it—and I've tried to

00:59:44.480 --> 00:59:48.870
really support this church and help them

00:59:48.880 --> 00:59:51.990
because they

00:59:52.000 --> 00:59:55.349
have a vision.

00:59:55.359 --> 00:59:58.950
So it's exciting. But

00:59:58.960 --> 01:00:00.230
the whole point of what I want to tell

01:00:00.240 --> 01:00:01.829
you all is this: you can't draw

01:00:01.839 --> 01:00:04.309
from a well that is dry. So, bless

01:00:04.319 --> 01:00:07.030
your local church. Help them.

01:00:07.040 --> 01:00:08.390
And the angels—you send them out and

01:00:08.400 --> 01:00:10.950
they'll bless you.

01:00:10.960 --> 01:00:14.870
You know that.

01:00:14.880 --> 01:00:16.710
Tonight, if you're here and you've

01:00:16.720 --> 01:00:18.549
never asked Jesus Christ to be your Lord

01:00:18.559 --> 01:00:20.710
and personal Savior, and you tell me,

01:00:20.720 --> 01:00:23.430
'Brandon, I'm not saved. I'm just

01:00:23.440 --> 01:00:25.270
watching you and I wanted to know what

01:00:25.280 --> 01:00:27.030
was being said in the news,

01:00:27.040 --> 01:00:29.510
but I'm feeling a

01:00:29.520 --> 01:00:31.990
tug on my heart tonight.'You say,

01:00:32.000 --> 01:00:34.390
'Brandon, I want to give my heart to

01:00:34.400 --> 01:00:36.470
Jesus Christ. I'm tired of

01:00:36.470 --> 01:00:36.480
running.'You

01:00:36.480 --> 01:00:38.309
may be at the end of your rope. You may

01:00:38.319 --> 01:00:40.470
be here tonight and you say, 'Brandon, I

01:00:40.480 --> 01:00:42.549
feel like self-harm. I feel like all

01:00:42.559 --> 01:00:44.309
these things. I feel so heavy. I've

01:00:44.319 --> 01:00:46.549
battled depression and anxiety. I've had

01:00:46.559 --> 01:00:49.430
the worst week from heck I could ever

01:00:49.440 --> 01:00:51.349
tell you about. I lost my job.'There are

01:00:51.359 --> 01:00:53.109
so many people that have so much going

01:00:53.119 --> 01:00:55.670
on. I got diagnosed with an

01:00:55.670 --> 01:00:55.680
incurable

01:00:55.680 --> 01:00:57.990
disease and I'm so broken. I just need

01:00:58.000 --> 01:01:00.150
somebody to pray for me. But tonight's

01:01:00.160 --> 01:01:02.630
the night you give Jesus Christ

01:01:02.640 --> 01:01:05.589
your heart. If you've never asked

01:01:05.599 --> 01:01:07.349
Jesus Christ to be your Lord and

01:01:07.359 --> 01:01:09.430
personal Savior, I want to give you the

01:01:09.440 --> 01:01:11.910
invitation and tell you there's a heaven

01:01:11.920 --> 01:01:14.630
to gain and a hell to shun.

01:01:14.640 --> 01:01:17.109
The very shoes you put on today to go to

01:01:17.119 --> 01:01:18.950
work, the undertaker might be taking

01:01:18.960 --> 01:01:21.829
them off

01:01:21.829 --> 01:01:21.839
tonight.

01:01:21.839 --> 01:01:23.910
No one's promised tomorrow, ladies and

01:01:23.920 --> 01:01:26.390
gentlemen. When we see the days

01:01:26.400 --> 01:01:27.829
approaching and there's so much

01:01:27.839 --> 01:01:30.309
darkness and so much going on right

01:01:30.319 --> 01:01:33.109
now,

01:01:33.119 --> 01:01:36.069
it's shocking when we

01:01:36.079 --> 01:01:38.950
watch the news.

01:01:38.960 --> 01:01:40.230
But you're going to have to be in the

01:01:40.240 --> 01:01:42.309
right place at the right time

01:01:42.319 --> 01:01:45.430
in the days ahead, because if you're

01:01:45.440 --> 01:01:47.990
not listening to the voice of the Lord,

01:01:48.000 --> 01:01:49.589
there's a great opportunity you could go

01:01:49.599 --> 01:01:51.990
home early. 'You're trying to scare me,

01:01:51.990 --> 01:01:52.000
Brandon.'No,

01:01:52.000 --> 01:01:54.470
